OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1777399865
OL,3,CSix jailed over #4m cannabis conspiracy
OL,5,FSix gang members involved in growing
OL,6,F#4 million of cannabis at sites across
OL,7,FWest Yorkshire have been jailed.
OL,9,FRingleader Selman Hysa and co-
OL,10,Fconspirators, including relatives,
OL,11,Fwere involved in the "industrial-scale
OL,12,Fproduction" of the drug in 2024 and
OL,13,F2025 West Yorkshire Police said.
OL,15,FOfficers found cannabis farms at
OL,16,FAlverthorpe Road, Wakefield, Newgate
OL,17,FHouse, Pontefract, Wakefield
OL,18,FCommercial Park and Beckbridge
OL,19,FIndustrial Estate, Normanton.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
