PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1777399865
OL,3,CSix jailed over #4m cannabis conspiracy
OL,5,FA fifth cannabis farm was found at the
OL,6,Fsite of the former Moldgreen Top Club,
OL,7,Fin Church Street, Huddersfield.
OL,9,FHysa, along with his nephews Armand
OL,10,Fand Klevis Hysa admitted conspiring to
OL,11,Fproduce cannabis, alongside Kosta
OL,12,FDumani and Admir Cerpja.
OL,14,FSelman Hysa also admitted money
OL,15,Flaundering offences, while Armand Hysa
OL,16,Fadmitted possession of cannabis with
OL,17,Fintent to supply, possession of
OL,18,Fcocaine, and money laundering offences.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
