CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1777399865
OL,3,CSix jailed over #4m cannabis conspiracy
OL,5,FSelman Hysa, 44, of Warmfield Lane,
OL,6,FWarmfield, Wakefield, was sentenced to
OL,7,Fsix years and six months.
OL,9,FArmand Hysa, 24, of Doncaster Road,
OL,10,FWakefield, was jailed for five years
OL,11,Fand three months.
OL,13,FKlevis Hysa, 29, of no fixed address,
OL,14,Freceived a sentence of four years and
OL,15,Fsix months.
OL,17,FKosta Dumani, 42, of no fixed address,
OL,18,Fwas sentenced to four years.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
