PN,36204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1777399865
OL,3,CSix jailed over #4m cannabis conspiracy
OL,5,FAdmir Cerpja, 43, of no fixed address
OL,6,Fwas jailed for three years and 11
OL,7,Fmonths.
OL,9,FA sixth man, 26-year-old Klodian
OL,10,FBofja, was sentenced to 16 months for
OL,11,Fcannabis production
OL,13,FDet Sgt Karl Heath said: "Our
OL,14,Finvestigation deliberately targeted
OL,15,Fthe leadership of this organised
OL,16,Fgroup. By targeting the very top tier,
OL,17,Fwe directly struck those who reap the
OL,18,Fgreatest rewards from criminality.
