OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1777399865
OL,3,CSix jailed over #4m cannabis conspiracy
OL,5,F"Large-scale cannabis production is
OL,6,Ffar from a victimless crime. It fuels
OL,7,Fwider organised crime and creates
OL,8,Fserious risk of harm to communities.
OL,9,FThose at the top profit substantially
OL,10,Ffrom these operations, which often
OL,11,Finvolve vulnerable people being
OL,12,Fexploited to live and work in unsafe,
OL,13,Foften squalid conditions."
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
